===Etymology===
From the {{bor|en|cmn-pinyin|-}} romanization of the {{bor|en|cmn|-}} Chinese pronunciation for {{zh-l|湖北}}, literally "north of the lake", referring to Hubei's position north of [[Dongting]] Lake.

